    v2 = 1.0

    v2 = (0.87 - ((v1 + 0.44 + v1 + 0.30) / (v0 + 0.64 * v1 + 0.75)))
    v0 = ((0.82 * wp.abs(v2 + 0.38)) / 0.33)
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.cos(v1 + 0.63) * v1))
    v0 = wp.exp(0.46)
    v0 = wp.abs(tmp)
